Cthulhu book?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You don't trust{nl}
Kuroori?{waitkey}{clearbox}Unlike the one in our town,{nl}
he seems to be quite{nl}
capable.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Yes, I'm fairly sure{nl}
