What the heck's that mean?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: We ran into that shady{nl}
old man again, huh.{waitkey}Elly: I do wish they'd display{nl}
a few more things about{nl}
Demons here.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: With the "Evil-Warding{nl}
Mirror," we can fight the{nl}
subway Demon, can't we?{waitkey}

Brown: With the "Evil-Warding{nl}
Mirror"!{wait_fr:32} I can actually fight{nl}
demons, huh...{waitkey}Ayase: What's this? {ctl0f:1},{nl}
you're more of a bookworm{nl}
